League of Shadows<br>
Temple of Terror<br>
Paineel<br>
<br>
Dear D'Ron Karr,<br>
<br>
I will be there, unarmed as you request.  Please look for me in the guise of a Teir'Dal, this should make your task a little easier.<br>
<br>
