League of Honour <p><img border=0 src="http://www.leagueofhonour.com/images/members/meledi-sig.jpg" /></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tanare>Tanare</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 215<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/19/03 9:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1193.topic&index=45>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Letter to Meledy singy person</span><hr size=1> ((ooc- sorry about the delay, been putting in longer hours at work sooner than i expected to...))<br>
<br>
 Tanare was rather happy to hear that she had a letter when the servant arrived in the room where she was still waiting for a fitting for her new dress. The servant for some reason refused to stay long , in fact he came in, tossed the note on the table and left saying nothing more than &quot;This is for you.&quot;<br>
<br>
  She was of course,completely unaware of the idea that the servants' fear to be exposed to her babbling for any extended period of time was indirectly the exact sort of fear Littany had hopes that Tanare herself would be feeling during her stay. Tanare however just thought there were lots of them around and they had to take turns because they all wanted to see just how cute she really was.<br>
<br>
   Openning the note Tanare sat down amidst the pelts, some of which actually had straight seams in them as her sewing had improved though her alcohol had run out and she feared for her sewing results without it. Smiling she realized it was from D'ron Karr <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>i knew evil dronky didn't kill him</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> she thought as she sat to read.<br>
<br>
   A few hours later, after many breaks from boredom as she tried to make her way through the lengthy letter- the same boredom of book reading which kept her from passing the druidic initiation testing when she was old enough to choose a profession- to her mother's dismay at the time though Tanare was not aware of that, she sat back and considered what she had read.<br>
<br>
   <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Hmm it sounds like Dronky and evil Dronky were like fighting and stuff. First he sounds like the nice dronky but then he sounds like the bad one, and he like even says his name a lot when he's writing like he's not really him or something.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> Tanare thought, the very effort threatening to overwhelm her brain. Then suddenly &quot;understanding&quot; dawned on her.<br>
<br>
   <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Oh I get it now.... there's only one dronky...BUT he like got hit in the head or something so he keeps forgetting if he's a pally guy or a shadowy knight guy so that's why he keeps writing his own name down so he can like remember who he is, unless he can't and thinks that he's someone else. Just like cousin Eddy who fell off the treehouse and thought he was a dwarf until someone else the orcy guy hit him in the head again...but then he throught he was an orc so he ran home with them and they like killed him... Poor Eddy.<br>
<br>
   Oh wait i was talking about Dronky, so since he got hit in the head- must have been one of those bad doggies, he keeps changing from pally guy to shadowy guy. I'll have to like help him and stuff. I STILL say they should just like write Cazicy god guy a letter asking for him to let them do that big word thingy to the temple. Maybe Lord Thule will know his address when he comes to the party, i wonder if Cazicy knows that Lord Thule has the same last name as him? But wait that Littany person has that same name too, maybe she's like his daughter or something. I don't know why Evil Dronky thinks i have to like die and stuff, that's silly. Oh i guess i should write back to Dronky, maybe pally Dronky will be awake when he gets it.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
   Coming to the table she took out a piece of paper and began to concentrate as she prepared to write her letter, as usual the tip of her tongue peeking out of the corner of her mouth as she wrote.<br>
<br>
   &quot;Dear Dronky<br>
<br>
   &quot;I knew evil Dronky didn't kill you like he said he would cause he said i wouldn't like see you again, but then you said you'd be at the moondarky party thingy. Anyways, I figured out that like there isn't two of you and stuff but i think you might need to see a healy person. Cause you like got hit in the head and stuff so now you think you're a pally guy and a shadowy guy, even though the shadowy guy person doesn't like the pally guy part so he says like mean stuff and ...stuff which being a pally guy you wouldn't do.<br>
<br>
  &quot;Oh for all the facty pointy things you said i like read them and realized that shadowy guy is like wrong and stuff. I saw shadowy you like tell the skele guy to like go away and it like exploded and stuff, just like evil you said pally guys do. And of course we went into the temple place of that cazic guy- why he keeps his temple in a dress shop i don;t know but that must be why he's like a gody guy and stuff. You figured since you had a mighty and tough ranger with you that we could like destroy the evil temple place  cause there WAS 2 of us and all, until we found out about the dress shop here.<br>
<br>
  &quot;I guess that temple stuff is like boring and all so that's why Littany person went into dress making cause she was bored and all and the Honory peopls probably made fun of her dresses before so she don't like them now so that's why she was making fun of my badge thingy the other day when we saw her. And you like wanted me to give her dresses a chance cause you felt bad for her like a pally guy does so you put the chain thingy on me so i wouldn't get bored and leave the shop before i got to try on the dress and all.<br>
<br>
  &quot;Then she's having a big party for her father Lord Thuley, see i didn't realize they were related til you wrote their names down so now i know why she wants to make sure the party is like perfect and stuff so she don't get her father mad. I guess he must be related to Cazicy guy even though most gody guys don't have kids...well Tunare did but Firiona doesn't like me cause she's jealous that i'm much cuter than she is, and i think she liked her mother's old name better before she changed it because she thought i was so cute.<br>
<br>
  &quot;Anyways, just cause i'll be cuter than all the other peoples there with my new dress is no reason for them to want to kill me even if they are jealous and stuff at how cute i am and stuff. Big foreheady peoples don't like getting dirty and if we like fought and stuff they'd have blood and stuff all over the place and mess up their dresses and suits and everything. Of course i'd win cause i AM a mighty and tough ranger and stuff.<br>
<br>
   &quot;But i don't know if you can be my date for the moondarky party though, mother doesn't like me going on dates and stuff with people she hasn't met first. Unless you want to go visit her and all. Just make sure you don't think you're shadowy Dronky though cause she'll like get mad and stuff. Last time she got mad was right before father died and she found him swimming with that snobby elf girl. I mean just because they left their clothes on the shore so they wouldn;t get wet while they were swimming wasn't any reason for mother to get mad i don't think. <br>
<br>
   &quot;Anyways she like fired a spell as the elfy girl did a magic poofy spell and then we heard that Crushy Emperor's castle like got blown apart by some big lightening bolt thingy and rocks and doors and towers went flying everywhere and smooshed some evil orcys too. Everyone said mother did it...father didn't come back home for a week for some reason but he brought lots of presents for us all when he did!<br>
<br>
   &quot;So anyways, try to go see a healy person so you can stop thinking your like shadowy guy and stuff. Maybe you should like try banging your head against a stone wall or something. I think someone told me that works sometimes.<br>
<br>
   &quot;Ok have to go back to my sewing so i can have a whole outfit finished for you when you like come by for the party. See you then byebye!<br>
<br>
    Tanare<br>
<br>
P.S.- don't worry i'm still cute as ever!&quot;<br>
<br>
  Smiling proudly at the end of her letter, not noticing the sweat on her forehead and the effort the letter writing took, she sealed it and wrote &quot;To Dronky&quot; on the outside and yelled for someone to come into the room. Realizing she wouldn't stop as the spell casters of Paineel began to mutter to themselves, the same servant hesitantly returned to the room.<br>
<br>
  &quot;Yes what are you yelling about?&quot; he asked.<br>
<br>
  &quot;Oh goodie you're like here and stuff. Anyways i have this letter i have to send to Dronky but i can't go without losing my place in line so could you like find the bardy peoples and give them the letter to them so they could like send it to him?&quot; she asked smiling brightly at the underling holding out the letter.<br>
<br>
   &quot;Um, yes of course.&quot; the servant replied taking the note and proceeding to turn around quickly and leave the room as Tanare's thanks echoed behind him.<br>
<br>
