<br>
She left the room, closing the door carefully behind her, and almost bumped into an unfamiliar form in the hallway. Her eyes narrowed, realizing this one was not of her Temple. Two words, and a spell of rooting, and another of fear shimmered like a wave of heat inside the corridor.<br>
<br>
&quot;And who are you pray tell&quot; she asked the stranger.<br>
