<br>
Startled that the shadowknight had discovered him and having discovered the news that he had come to find, the seemingly erudite servant dropped his invisibility spell and bowed, evidently cowed, to the knight.  Waiting till the knight rounded the corner and was out of earshot, Oligith hastily pulled a quill and parchment out of his pack and penned a fast note.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Meledi and Tanare,<br>
The League of Honour shall know of your location shortly, and we will bring all of our allies down upon Paineel if necessary to free you from this captivity.  Never fear.<br>
<br>
Oligith</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
Wishing he could do something to comfort the captive in the adjacent cell, but not wishing to do anything to alert the guards further, Oligith proceeded down the hallway out of their sight.  After rounding the corner, he concentrated and cast two quick spells making both of the guards very passive and unaware of the happenings around them.<br>
<br>
The enchanter sped to the door where Meledi and Tanare could be heard speaking....Tanare rather loudly still...and slipped the note under it.  Knocking once, Oligith began the incantations to open a portal to New Tanaan where his essence was bound.  He stepped through breathing a prayer to Karana that the two would be safe till his return. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.leagueofhonour.com/images/members/oligith.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Sage Koada'dal Phantasmist of the 64th Circle<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>  Elf of Many Faces</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=425188">Equipment</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> | <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.geocities.com/lsteim/OgHist.html">Stories</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=rhaxalygen>Rhaxalygen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 339<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/24/03 9:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1193.topic&index=60>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Letter to Meledy singy person</span><hr size=1> Aurwena, clad only in her underpadding in her damp,<br>
chilly cell, was wondering what D'ron Karr planned<br>
to do with her. She was still ashamed of herself<br>
for ever thinking that the young man would help<br>
her, and yet the young Wood Elf felt that she<br>
was not really to blame. Most fighters at least<br>
had SOME sense of honor if they were not Dark<br>
Elves, Ogres, Trolls, or Iksar. Alas, her assumption <br>
had cost her dearly...<br>
<br>
Suddenly, a tiny slit in the cell door opened,<br>
letting in light. &quot;Milady?&quot; said Jobarnik, one<br>
of Paineel's skeletal servants. &quot;Your breakfast<br>
is here. I shall slide it through this slot to you.&quot; <br>
<br>
Aurwena picked up the bread, cheese, and water<br>
as best she could with her shackles on and began<br>
to eat. &quot;How much longer will I stay alive?&quot; she <br>
wondered. &quot;Is Tanare still to be sacrificed to Cazic-<br>
Thule at the Ceremony of the Moondark, or will it<br>
be I who suffers this terrible fate?&quot; She shivered. <br>
<br>
&quot;I have to wait for that Dron' Karr to tell me, or l<br>
someone from the Temple proper. By Zeboxurok,<br>
I sure hope Meledi, that Bard, has some plan<br>
to rescue Tanare! If not, we may both be utterly<br>
doomed!&quot; The young girl finished her meal and sighed. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=1193.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=1193.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=1193.topic&start=61&stop=76>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=1193.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showNextMessage?topicID=1193.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1193.topic&index=60><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.threadControl?topicID=1193.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1193.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1193.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="